ACK 2bf7183ea9b42a9edf76bccdf00708341a1d2c0a

Indeed, there is no debug log warning yet as suggested in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/27869#pullrequestreview-1477293036.

Sanity check:

```json
$ ./src/bitcoin-cli -signet listwallets                 
[
  "sqlite3",
  "bdb"
]
$ ./src/bitcoin-cli -signet unloadwallet bdb            
{
}
$ ./src/bitcoin-cli -signet loadwallet bdb            
{
  "name": "bdb",
  "warnings": [
    "Wallet loaded successfully. The legacy wallet type is being deprecated and support for creating and opening legacy wallets will be removed in the future. Legacy wallets can be migrated to a descriptor wallet with migratewallet."
  ]
}
```

